# tsconfig.json

## Include/Exclude (righe 2-3)
- include: ["client/src/**/*", "shared/**/*", "server/**/*"]
- exclude: ["node_modules", "build", "dist", "**/*.test.ts", "legacy/**/*"]

## CompilerOptions (righe 4-22)
- noEmit: true
- module: "ESNext"
- strict: true
- jsx: "preserve"
- moduleResolution: "bundler"
- allowImportingTsExtensions: true

## Paths (righe 18-21)
- "@/*": ["./client/src/*"]
- "@shared/*": ["./shared/*"]
